item.title: HELP! pleasee
item.dc:creator: @Saphire1 Saphire`
item.description:
@Saphire1 wrote:

Your server doesn’t recognize those commands because that haven’t been declared.

Put this under the main void.

public void sendMessage(String s) { outStream.createFrameVarSize(253); outStream.writeString(s); outStream.endFrameVarSize(); }

and try and fine the correct teleport variable you are currently using, then replace.
